glxosd (1.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Changed the plugin loading mechanics to stop libraries from being inserted
  into memory more than once. Fixes crashes when the configuration files are
  missing.

 -- Nick Guletskii <nickguletskii200@gmail.com>  Thu, 26 Dec 2013 11:09:32 +0300

glxosd (1.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Made the launcher more dynamic by making it scan for libraries to inject.
  * Add NVIDIA sensor support for installations done through dpkg.
  * Split libsensors and NVIDIA sensor support into a different shared library.

 -- Nick Guletskii <nickguletskii200@gmail.com>  Tue, 17 Dec 2013 23:26:07 +0300

